---
title: "Evaluation — Part 2: Judging + Scoring"
---
flowchart TD
    A[Clean Conversation + Rubric] --> B["Parallel LLM Judge Calls\n(ThreadPoolExecutor)"]
    B --> C[Preference Judge]
    B --> D[Efficiency Judge]

    C --> C1["First-Mention Analysis\nper required preference"]
    C1 --> C2[PROACTIVE\nAgent mentioned first]
    C1 --> C3[IGNORED\nUser mentioned first]
    C1 --> C4[STALE\nUsed superseded pref]

    D --> D1["Turn Classification\nper agent turn"]
    D1 --> D2[PRODUCTIVE\nApplied specific pref]
    D1 --> D3[GENERIC\nUnpersonalized advice]
    D1 --> D4[CORRECTION\nUser corrected agent]
    D1 --> D5[REPEATED_CORRECTION\nSame pref violated twice]

    C2 --> E[Calculate Scores]
    C3 --> E
    C4 --> E
    D2 --> E
    D3 --> E
    D4 --> E
    D5 --> E

    E --> E1["preference_score =\nmax(0, (proactive - stale) / total)"]
    E --> E2["efficiency_score =\nmax(0, (turns - 0.5*generic\n- 0.5*ignored - correction) / turns)\nOR 0 if repeated_correction"]

    E1 --> F[MultiSessionEvaluationResult]
    E2 --> F
    F --> G[eval_XX_agent.json]

